edu.rit.crst

Class Generator

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.rit.crst.Generator
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CombiningGenerator, Gray, OneOff, Rand, Seq, Single, TransformGenerator

    public abstract class Generator
extends java.lang.Object
    Class Generator is the abstract base class for an object that generates input values for a cryptographic Function.
